    "user_reviews": [
      {
        "title": "Upgraded my motherboard so I could use this CPU for 4K gaming. Its £100 more than the i5 9400F I ...",
        "text": "Upgraded my motherboard so I could use this CPU for 4K gaming. Its £100 more than the i5 9400F I had but the difference in performance is quite extreme. Without changing any GPU (2080 Super) settings, the GPU runs much cooler and quieter at 2K with ultra settings and 4K with high settings at 60fps with HDR. No overclocking necessary so far. It is worth the investment for a decent gaming experience. No more judder or stutter. Its also more than sufficient for 4K video editing with this GPU. Very happy with this CPU and glad I did my research this time.",
        "user_name": "B.B.",
        "source": "homeessentialsdirect.com",
        "rating": 5,
